            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/krd/press/press-releases/2010/New-rental-funding-for-regulated-housing-tenants-in-Trondheim.html?id=604480" title="">
                        New rental funding for regulated housing tenants in Trondheim
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[12.05.2010]</p>
                <p>Rental regulation for pre-war housing was phased out in the New Year. In a revised national budget, the Government issues a bill on new housing rental funding for occupants who are unable to pay current rents for such housing in Trondheim. This funding will be means-tested.</p>
                
                
